{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Let yourself be immersed by the colorful and nostalgic universe of board games. Find the dark mystery that lies beneath the facade of a pleasant and idyllic world and solve it to restore peace to the land of board games before it is consumed by the plague. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/extras/roll-banner.png?t=1729720291\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/extras/roll.gif?t=1729720291\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are the die, therefore your strongest weapon is rolling. Perform rolls to avoid enemy attacks while also changing and reloading weapons. You have 4 slots that you can fill with a variety of crazy arsenal. As each attempt is different, you can approach this game in any way you like! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/extras/combine-banner.png?t=1729720291\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/extras/0000_2.gif?t=1729720291\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover new weapons and modify them with passive effects to create completely different versions. Modify your equipment in any way you want to find your favorite combinations and become unbeatable on the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/extras/fight-banner.png?t=1729720291\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/extras/fight.gif?t=1729720291\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse the board game cabinet and battle with numerous unique enemies. At the end of each floor, a challenging boss awaits you. Will you head straight towards him, or explore in search of gear that can even the odds?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready, this once beautiful realm needs a hero - an unassuming die which will fight, die, and return to do it once again. The world is not going to save itself, you know.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729720291","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/page.bg.jpg?t=1729720291","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729720291","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729720291","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Let yourself be immersed by the colorful and nostalgic universe of board games. Find the dark mystery that lies beneath the facade of a pleasant and idyllic world and solve it to restore peace to the land of board games before it is consumed by the plague. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/extras/roll-banner.png?t=1729720291\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987810/extras/roll.gif?t=1729720291\" /></p